# Lesson Plans

This folder stores lesson planning materials for VCE English. It is intended to support day-to-day teaching, unit sequencing, workshop planning, revision lessons, and reusable class activities.

## Purpose

The purpose of this folder is to keep lesson planning organised, practical, and reusable. It should help reduce repeated planning work across terms and make it easier to refine lessons over time.

This folder can be used to store:
- Weekly lesson plans.
- Individual lesson outlines.
- Skills workshops.
- Revision sessions.
- Exam preparation lessons.
- Differentiated class activities.
- Teacher notes for explicit instruction.

## Suggested structure

```text
Lesson-Plans/
├── README.md
├── Weekly-Plans/
├── Single-Lessons/
├── Workshops/
├── Revision/
└── Templates/
```

